Chrome/90.0.4430.70 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 981.183, "format": "dash-1260180476037045v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}, {"format_id": "dash-26186329590963242v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1549.165, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQOqS9qbMvfsnzOgZvFTrEMi5tFPBLB7Q4cQZO7ZTJWDOjvTawHK63CugwI3wUcEac_h93fXX0txoCt9_c2CHu2VHa9Neae57KufPd8.mp4?_nc_cat=102&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=1SzR-j5s4PsQ7kNvwH8FdML&&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=AW_bAlXybP4fuEex3GrrXQ&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af24JpUyn2-rrr989TQKtJhX7JvZX5okbZ1tpM58d95_Ng&oe=69DA293B", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 1684716, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/90.0.4430.70 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1549.165, "format": "dash-26186329590963242v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by naturalwarrior", "description": "‼️These studies stopped me in my tracks‼️\n\nScientists tested a completely natural compound formed from ancient soil and peat - and what they observed under the microscope was remarkable.\n\nResearchers exposed human melanoma (skin cancer) cells to humic and fulvic acids, naturally occurring compounds created over thousands of years in the earth.\n\nWhat happened next was wild\n⏱️ Within just 14 hours:\n🧬 Growth signals were switched OFF\n⚠️ Death signals were switched ON\n💥 Cancer cells stopped multiplying and entered programmed cell death (apoptosis)\n\nThe cells didn’t just slow down - they collapsed, as if the body remembered how to shut down damaged cells.\n\nAnd here’s the part that gave me goosebumps 👀\nThe same compounds also reduced the gene responsible for melanin production, meaning they supported clearer, brighter, more even-looking skin -  naturally.*\nOne compound.\nFrom the earth itself.\nSupporting both cellular health and skin clarity.\nSo tell me… why isn’t this front-page news?\n\nComment “FULVIC” if you’d like the direct link to the fulvic mineral blend I personally use.\n\n📚 Study reference (peer-reviewed):\nSalehi et al., 2022\n“Activation of apoptosis and G0/G1 cell cycle arrest along with inhibition of melanogenesis by humic acid and fulvic acid in A375 human melanoma cells.”\n🔗 PubMed: https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35656077/\n\n(Not medical advice)", "duration": 8.7, "timestamp": 1772485282, "uploader_id": "27773725102", "uploader": "Greg Madder", "channel": "naturalwarrior", "like_count": 1286, "comment_count": 570, "comments": [{"author": "rmeza.d.r84", "author_id": "80179544079", "id": "18100773418787417", "text": "Wtf is it dam, let me guess,  there's a pay wall 🧱", "timestamp": 1775506410}, {"author": "evanegas04", "author_id": "212362961", "id": "18574313080005854", "text": "Fulvic", "timestamp": 1775505577}, {"author": "ingrid.wolf24", "author_id": "22572035716", "id": "17949540546134717", "text": "Fulvic", "timestamp": 1775503917}, {"author": "marbie.mtop", "author_id": "76956358773", "id": "18077569724398989", "text": "Fulvic", "timestamp": 1775501060}, {"author": "mapuii_daniel_mom", "author_id": "8362832507", "id": "18336084889170826", "text": "Fulvic", "timestamp": 1775500444}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-